EDF May Offer EU1.15 to EU1.3 a Share for Edison, Sole Says

-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-10-23T10:46:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/edf-may-offer-eu1-15-to-eu1-3-a-share-for-edison-sole-says.html
EDF SA (EDF)  may offer  Edison SpA (EDN) ’s
Italian investors between 1.15 euros ($1.60) and 1.3 euros a
share for their stake in the holding company that controls 30
percent of the Italian utility, daily  Il Sole 24 Ore  reported
without saying how it got the information.  The offer may also include additional assets such as
Edison’s hydroelectric plants, Sole said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  